<subSubSection id="FEB4EF82FF85FFDFFF07F97DAF24F954" pageId="11" pageNumber="327" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="B611BC09FF85FFDFFF07F97DAF24F954" blockId="11.[151,1437,909,1801]" pageId="11" pageNumber="327">
<emphasis id="84DA601BFF85FFDFFF07F97DAF50F92C" bold="true" box="[199,335,1668,1693]" pageId="11" pageNumber="327">Comments.</emphasis>
This species is distinguished by its coloration, with yellow head, brown antenna with white annulus at the apex, mesosoma dark brown with lighter propodeum and the first tergum of metasoma light brown and granulose.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="FEB4EF82FF85FFDFFF07F909AB82F8B8" box="[199,1437,1776,1801]" pageId="11" pageNumber="327" type="etymology">
